ffmpegthumbnailer: ffmpegthumbnailer (lightweight video thumbnailer)
ffmpegthumbnailer:
ffmpegthumbnailer: This video thumbnailer can be used to create thumbnails for your
ffmpegthumbnailer: video files. The thumbnailer uses ffmpeg to decode frames from the
ffmpegthumbnailer: video files, so supported videoformats depend on the configuration
ffmpegthumbnailer: flags of ffmpeg.
ffmpegthumbnailer: This thumbnailer was designed to be as fast and lightweight as
ffmpegthumbnailer: possible. The only dependencies are ffmpeg, libpng and libjpeg. 
ffmpegthumbnailer:
ffmpegthumbnailer: http://code.google.com/p/ffmpegthumbnailer/
